Around 7:30 a.m. on Saturday , May 17 , Lowell resident Alexander Dlouhy was driving a Volkswagen Jetta north on Lincoln Lake Ave .
when the car crossed the center line , according to the Kent County Sheriff 's Department .
The car collided with a southbound Ford Explorer .
Dlouhy , who was not wearing a seat belt , died at the scene .
